casebody.data:
Scott A. HUMINSKI, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
TOWN OF GILBERT, Arizona, et al., Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D17-4740 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. December 20, 2017

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Petitioner's petition and supplement to petition are denied.

Petitioner's motion to stay is denied.

Petitioner's motion and supplement to motion to enjoin orders are denied.

Petitioner's motion and second motion for assistance of counsel are denied.

VILLANTI, KHOUZAM, and SLEET, JJ., Concur.
